    "body": "lodestar does catch the invalid block\r\n\r\n```\r\nAug-14 17:21:00.665[NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: Received gossip block slot=3665805, root=0x608eâ€¦8c93, curentSlot=3665805, peerId=bafzaajiiaijccav37zyt7s5jgx2vkdtuclgnagytf6ci2s7a6zz3iufzac5q24iv3a, delaySec=0.6570000648498535\r\nAug-14 17:21:02.310[CHAIN]           ^[[31merror^[[39m: Block error slot=3665805, errCode=BLOCK_ERROR_EXECUTION_ERROR BLOCK_ERROR_EXECUTION_ERROR\r\nError: BLOCK_ERROR_EXECUTION_ERROR\r\n    at verifyBlockExecutionPayload (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/verifyBlocksExecutionPayloads.ts:298:13)\r\n    at runMicrotasks (<anonymous>)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:96:5)\r\n    at verifyBlocksExecutionPayload (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/verifyBlocksExecutionPayloads.ts:124:31)\r\n    at async Promise.all (index 2)\r\n    at BeaconChain.verifyBlocksInEpoch (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/verifyBlock.ts:67:91)\r\n    at BeaconChain.processBlocks (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/index.ts:71:68)\r\n    at Timeout.JobItemQueue.runJob [as _onTimeout] (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/util/queue/itemQueue.ts:92:22)\r\nAug-14 17:21:02.311[NETWORK]         ^[[31merror^[[39m: Error receiving block slot=3665805, peer=bafzaajiiaijccav37zyt7s5jgx2vkdtuclgnagytf6ci2s7a6zz3iufzac5q24iv3a code=BLOCK_ERROR_EXECUTION_ERROR, execStatus=INVALID_BLOCK_HASH, errorMessage=Malformed block\r\nError: BLOCK_ERROR_EXECUTION_ERROR\r\n    at verifyBlockExecutionPayload (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/verifyBlocksExecutionPayloads.ts:298:13)\r\n    at runMicrotasks (<anonymous>)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:96:5)\r\n    at verifyBlocksExecutionPayload (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/verifyBlocksExecutionPayloads.ts:124:31)\r\n    at async Promise.all (index 2)\r\n    at BeaconChain.verifyBlocksInEpoch (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/verifyBlock.ts:67:91)\r\n    at BeaconChain.processBlocks (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/index.ts:71:68)\r\n    at Timeout.JobItemQueue.runJob [as _onTimeout] (file:///usr/app/packages/beacon-node/src/util/queue/itemQueue.ts:92:22)\r\n```\r\nit means the `beacon_aggregate_and_proof` message should be IGNORED since the head block is not in forkchoice\r\n\r\nI think the message was sent to peers through control mechanism (IHAVE/IWANT), there was a bug that libp2p-gossipsub sent not validated messages https://github.com/ChainSafe/js-libp2p-gossipsub/pull/277\r\n\r\nall of lodestar nodes use libp2p-gossipsub 0.14.0 so it does not have the fix",
